rivalcfg-gui (1.4.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Release 1.4.0.
  * Fix Debian packaging: bundle standalone rivalcfg binary instead of
    depending on unavailable python3-rivalcfg package.
  * Add wget build-dependency for downloading standalone rivalcfg.
  * Change Architecture from 'all' to 'amd64' (bundled binary is x86_64).
  * Add SCRIPT_DIR / _find_rivalcfg() logic: the GUI now prefers a
    bundled rivalcfg binary in its own directory, falling back to PATH.

 -- MrGodzilla38 <oyunustasigodzilla@gmail.com>  Sat, 20 Jun 2026 08:17:24 +0000

